right?
M: That’s fine with me.
W: And if you don’t get the Ring Back Tone service, 
your monthly rate will be lower. 
M: That’s good. In fact, I don’t think it’s necessary.
W: All right, sir. We have a perfect plan to meet all 
your requirements.
M: Then, can I change to the service from now on?
W: Certainly, sir. If you don’t like it, you can change it 
any time after one month.
